lead_paragraph: Chelsea and former manager Jose Mourinho have reached an undisclosed settlement with former team doctor Eva Carneiro at an employment tribunal in London, the Premier League club said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea and Mourinho Settle With Former Doctor
